          "line_start": 6,
          "line_end": 26,
          "note": "Declares the Android 12+ BLE runtime permissions and the bluetooth_le + vulkan features, then the activity. The key line is the meta-data android.app.lib_name = onlychess: that tells NativeActivity which .so to load and run android_main from.",
          "note_comments": [],
          "code_comments": []
        },
        {
          "id": "01KV0QMWDR5H0AADBX6Z9CMDYG",
