          "code_path": "Games/Chess/Android/app/build.gradle.kts",
          "line_start": 28,
          "line_end": 33,
          "note": "externalNativeBuild points Gradle at our own CMakeLists. abiFilters target arm64 (devices) + x86_64 (emulator); ANDROID_STL is c++_static. ndkVersion/compileSdk are pinned and may need to match whatever SDK you install. Note: zero dependencies block.",
          "note_comments": [],
          "code_comments": []
        },
        {
          "id": "01KV0QMWDR5H0AADBX6Z9CMDYH",
