          "note": "On APP_CMD_INIT_WINDOW it creates the renderer against the ANativeWindow, then runs a smoke test of the shared core: GenerateLegalMoves from the start position should log 20. That line is the proof the perft-verified engine cross-compiles and runs under the NDK.",
