          "note": "The C++ side of the seam: an ITransport whose Send() will JNI-call BleShim.send, and whose Java_..._nativeOnReceived JNI entry will feed received bytes to the net layer. Stubbed now (task #8) — but this is where the platform radio meets the platform-neutral engine.",
